node.text: Casual Sunday in the neighborhood.
Just a month ago in this paradise!
Keep running 🦁
Pardon my back!

I have the fortune to have a father that always taught me: keep dreaming, keep believing, keep running and never give up. This is how from growing in a small city in the south of Italy you can end up waking up everyday at 6:00am in the amazing NYC and be able to build multiple million dollar companies at the age of 25. My motivation to overcome daily obstacles on the way is the energy and happiness of my family, friend and business partners that surround me. Never let anybody put you down, never stop chasing your dreams. Be positive, thankful and grateful.
